text: Padam Hang Thamsunhang also known as Sabin Limbu is a Nepali singer, musician and composer. He was born in Jhapa, Nepal. He started his musical career in 2009. ==Award and Nominations== * Genius Music Award 2022 * Epic Music Award * Box Office Music Award == Musical Concerts== * Cyprus * Rainbow Concert ==References== Category:Living people Category:1989 births Category:Nepalese singers
title: Sabin Limbu
